ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectBaffinland Iron Mines Corporation ** Lease of Territorial Land **
PrecisOrder authorizing BAFFINLAND IRON MINES CORPORATION to lease approximately 95,496 acres (38,646 hectares) of territorial land, for developing a port and railway to support the operation of the first iron mine in NUNAVUT.
